  <p>Emphatic and reflexive personal pronouns</p> -->

  <p>Infinitivals are used in the following very commonly used constructions – <ul>
      <li>the modal verbs eg. <m>feumaidh mi an leabhar a leughadh</m>
        <en>I have to read the book</en></li>
      <li>the <a href="?gd=rach"><g>rach</g></a> passive eg. <m>chaidh an leabhar a leughadh</m>
        <en>the book was read</en></li>
    </ul>
  </p>


